Alice Sweetwater's
Bar & Grille
opened its doors in December 1988. Ever since then, Alice Sweetwater’s has become a southwest Florida institution.
Some of the staff may have changed, Naples may have grown a little bigger, and the restaurant has changed decor, but the same values from 1988 still stand; serving great food to great people!
Today, Alice Sweetwater's is the local choice for fresh seafood, tasty delights from the grill, and everything in between. Our staff is always ready to serve with a friendly smile and helpful suggestion. Pair our customer service with
award-winning meals
and you have a recipe for success!
Enjoy a cozy atmosphere that welcomes locals, tourists, family and friends. We are not the cookie-cutter chain restaurant that fills up plazas around town; we're the real deal.
Check out our menu and stop by to see what we're all about! In the mood for a night in? Let us take care of dinner with Alice Sweetwater's Take Out! There's no reason you shouldn't eat heartily!
End Section 2
